{"tid":422910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人生痱滋生咗一個月","createTime":"2017-10-03T12:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T13:40:05.000Z","uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"946a796785486780ababd729fc730d0adb7c8031","tid":422910,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"粒痱滋成個月唔好,飲涼茶都仲係到<br />\n上網睇話可能係口腔癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴\\絲有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676a6aff8af935abfe66fe3a6fcb78c33d3cc27b","tid":422910,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306bb19254002c64621bcc3d1426b51472e77e68","tid":422910,"uid":150935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痱滋亦即口腔潰瘍，因黏膜缺損引致，成病原因眾多，包括口水分泌不足、電療後細胞萎縮、維他命B12不足、免疫系統疾病，或過濾性病毒如疱疹等。<br />\n<br />\nJoe（化名）25歲，不煙不酒，亦無過敏前科，由20歲起常生痱滋，兩年前愈趨頻密，每周都長出，有時更影響進食。痱滋面積可達一毫子硬幣大小，每次可長兩三粒；後來連腿部也有皮疹及陰囊潰瘍，他才認真求醫，並確診為白塞氏症。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/痱滋密密生%20%20惡疾悄悄來？-口腔癌免疫病先兆/web_tc/article/20150309/s00005/1425838124715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%97%B1%E6%BB%8B%E5%AF%86%E5%AF%86%E7%94%9F%2520%2520%E6%83%A1%E7%96%BE%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E4%BE%86%EF%BC%9F-%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%99%8C%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E7%97%85%E5%85%88%E5%85%86%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150309%2Fs00005%2F1425838124715&d=levEHzUdWgGqJdANtP16Shv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8fe0f72d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%97%B1%E6%BB%8B%E5%AF%86%E5%AF%86%E7%94%9F%2520%2520%E6%83%A1%E7%96%BE%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E4%BE%86%EF%BC%9F-%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%99%8C%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E7%97%85%E5%85%88%E5%85%86%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150309%2Fs00005%2F1425838124715&h=4908e069\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/痱滋密密生%20%20惡疾悄悄來？-口腔癌免疫病先兆/web_tc/article/20150309/s00005/1425838124715</a>"},{"pid":"26ee85abe8e01884a2077626ee91bc7e3686a1e1","tid":422910,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916b8358894146e0778c51f569c3b0052060f174","tid":422910,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"之前不停生痱滋, 一個月得幾日係冇生痱滋, 一好返冇耐又咬到咀,即刻灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後試下食左兩三個禮拜維他命B2 , 又真係少左生痱滋, 食多左熱氣野都冇事"},{"pid":"5b314c14598e20ed4be465779269cab88f59dc3a","tid":422910,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前不停生痱滋, 一個月得幾日係冇生痱滋, 一好返冇耐又咬到咀,即刻灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後試下食左兩三個禮拜維他命B2 , 又真係少左生痱滋, 食多左熱氣野都冇事</blockquote><br />\n我已經食少咗熱氣野都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}